Inside the box:
Small fish: tuna straws, fish net, dried squid, squid shavings, dried whale, octopus, dried cod, Shanghai squid;
Cheese: salted suluguni pigtail;
Meat: pickled ears;
Nuts: cashews in spicy glaze, peanuts;
Miscellaneous: Pringles chips, pita chips, Spanish Chorizo ​​sausage chips, Bake Rolls, Bretzil straws, potato straws.

All at once! This is about our beer box. It has everything for a spontaneous beer party at your place, at a party or in nature. Inside - cheese, fish, meat, chips, nuts and more. Maximum energy value, so that the party does not end until the night. And remember - you don’t have to wash the dishes!

Inside the box:
Sausages: salami with Parmigiano, real Parma ham, Italian cooked pork sausage Mortadella, spicy Spanish sausage Chorizo;
Meat: fried chicken fillet on skewers;
Compliments: baby mozzarella, hummus, pickled cherry tomatoes, gherkins, Kalamata olives, crispy dark and white croutons.

Now someone will regret becoming a vegan! In our meat box there are types of sausages for every day of the week. Monday - Salami with Parmigiano. Tuesday - Parma ham. Wednesday - Italian boiled pork sausage Mortadella. Thursday - Spicy Spanish Chorizo. Weekend - fried chicken fillet on skewers for the whole company!
